<B>__{federales}
<A>__{burst into the courtyard. two men hastily build a stack of boxes, etc., against the wall.}
<B>__{gordy}
<A>__{runs as fast as he can across the rooftops, when... a section of roof gives way beneath his feet, just as...}
<B>__{new angle}
<A>__{one of the federales finally mounts the wall, looks across the rooftops... and gordy's gone.}
<B>__{gordy}
<A>__{lands inside a warehouse room amid sacks of rice, beans and coffee. the building is dark and dusty. he lies still and listens. footsteps approach across the tin roof overhead. gordy burrows into the bags of rice, pulls them over him.}
<B>__{federale}
<A>__{on the roof peers down through the hole. scans the warehouse room below with a mini mag lite.}
<B>__{gordy}
<A>__{sees the flashlight beam move past. he holds his breath. beat. then the footsteps pass on, recede down the roof. and gordy can breathe again.}
